    "On the other hand, if the number of sentences gets too large, its ability to correctly classify sentences decreases.",
    "We find a similar bell-shaped relation for level 1 and level 2 (see Appendix section D).",
    "Taken these points into consideration, we opt for 10 sentences per prompt on all three levels.",
